---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import myImage from "../assets/about.jpg";
import SectionTitle from "./SectionTitle.astro";
---

<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24" id="about">
  <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-start">
    <!-- Image Container - Takes 5 columns -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:sticky lg:top-24">
      <div class="relative mx-auto lg:mx-0">
        <div class="aspect-[4/5]">
          <Image
            src={myImage}
            alt="Jake Meyers - AI Developer"
            class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
          />
        </div>
        <div
          class="absolute -z-10 -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-2xl opacity-70 blur-2xl"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Text Container - Takes 7 columns -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8">
      <SectionTitle title="About" />
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
        <p>
          Welcome to [Your Agency Name], your trusted partner in AI development and consulting, based in St. Louis, Missouri. We specialize in creating custom artificial intelligence solutions for businesses of all sizes, from local enterprises to Fortune 500 companies, and serve clients across the globe.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Our Expertise</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 mt-1 mr-3 bg-blue-100 rounded-full">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span>
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) applications:</strong> Supercharge your data access and decision-making.
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 mt-1 mr-3 bg-blue-100 rounded-full">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span>
              <strong class="text-gray-900">AI agents:</strong> Automate workflows and enhance productivity with intelligent tools.
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 mt-1 mr-3 bg-blue-100 rounded-full">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span>
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Custom chatbots:</strong> Deliver exceptional customer service 24/7 with tailored conversational AI.
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-8">
          Founded by Jake Meyers, a seasoned AI consultant and developer, we combine years of experience with cutting-edge technology to provide personalized solutions that deliver measurable results. Whether you're looking to streamline operations, enhance customer engagement, or unlock new revenue streams, our AI solutions are designed to align perfectly with your business goals.
        </p>

        <p>
          While we're proudly rooted in St. Louis, Missouri, our services extend to clients worldwide. At [Your Agency Name], we take a boutique approach, offering the care and attention of a small agency with the capabilities of an enterprise-grade partner.
        </p>

        <p>
          When we're not building AI solutions, you might find us exploring the beautiful trails around St. Louis, experimenting with the latest AI advancements, or planning our next innovation.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-12">
          <a
            href="#contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 text-base font-medium text-white bg-blue-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            Let's Work Together
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-5 h-5"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
              fill="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>